Symbol.Script_3D:
! Fire Detect and Alarm Equipment
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN END
res = 24 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN res = 8 ! Simple
IF useSysMat THEN MainBoxMaterial = sMat MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial PEN gs_cont_pen RESOL res
! --- FIRE DETECTION AND ALARM EQUIPMENT --- !
unID = 1 IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN ! Detailed IF objType = 1 THEN ! Alarm Pressure Switch CYLIND neckH, ConWidth_1 ADD -A/2, -A/2, neckH
HOTSPOT A, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
BLOCK A, B, bottomThk
ADDz bottomThk hh = ZZYZX - neckH - bottomThk FPRISM_ MainBoxMaterial, MainBoxMaterial, MainBoxMaterial, MainBoxMaterial, 4,hh, 90-alpha, hh, dx, dx, 15, dx, B-dx, 15, A-dx, B-dx, 15, A-dx, dx, 15 LIN_ A-dx2, dx2, hh, A-dx2, B-dx2, hh DEL 2 ENDIF
IF objType = 2 THEN ! Water Flow Indicator ROTy 90 CIRCLE ConWidth_1/2 DEL 1
ROTz 90 ROTx 90 ADDz -0.4*A
hy1 = 0.20*ConWidth_1 hy2 = 0.60*ConWidth_1 hy22= 0.52*ConWidth_1 hy3 = 0.80*ConWidth_1 hx = SQR((ConWidth_1/2)^2-hy1^2)
PRISM_ 13, 0.8*A, -B/2+hy1, hy1, 15, -B/2, hy22, 15, -B/2, hy2, 15, -ConWidth_1/2, hy2, 15, -ConWidth_1/3, hy3, 15, ConWidth_1/3, hy3, 15, ConWidth_1/2, hy2, 15, B/2, hy2, 15, B/2, hy22, 15, B/2-hy1, hy1, 15, hx, hy1, 79, 0,0,979, -hx, hy1, 3015 DEL 3
TOLER 0.003 RR = 0.08*ConWidth_1 ROTx 180 REVOLVE 2,180,1+2+16+32, 0,0.55*ConWidth_1+RR, 901, RR,360,4001 DEL 1 ADDy 0.55*ConWidth_1+RR CYLIND hy1, RR DEL 1 ADDy -0.55*ConWidth_1-RR CYLIND hy1, RR DEL 1
ADDz hy3 CYLIND 0.1*ZZYZX,0.25*A ADDz 0.1*ZZYZX ROTx 90 ROTy 90 ADDz -A/2
RESOL 12 R = ZZYZX/10 PRISM_ 9,A, -meterW/2, R, 79, -meterW/2, 0.9*ZZYZX-hy3-R, 79, -meterW/2+R, 0.9*ZZYZX-hy3, 1079, meterW/2-R, 0.9*ZZYZX-hy3, 79, meterW/2, 0.9*ZZYZX-hy3-R, 1079, meterW/2, R, 79, meterW/2-R, 0, 1079, -meterW/2+R, 0, 79, -meterW/2, R, 1079 DEL 5 ENDIF
IF objType = 3 THEN ! Water Motor Alarm tck = 0.1*A
ADDz ZZYZX-B/2 ROTy 90 ADDz -A/2 CYLIND tck, B/2 DEL 2
ROTy 90 ADDz -A/2+tck ROTz 90 HOTSPOT 0,B/2,0, unID: unID=unID+1 PRISM_ 4,0.9*A, -0.47*B, -ZZYZX+B/2, 15, -0.47*B, 0, 79, 0.47*B, 0, 1079, 0.47*B, -ZZYZX+B/2, 15 DEL 3 ENDIF ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN ! Simple IF objType = 1 THEN ! Alarm Pressure Switch CYLIND neckH, ConWidth_1 ADD -A/2, -A/2, neckH
HOTSPOT A, 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT A, B, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0, B, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1
hh = ZZYZX - neckH FPRISM_ MainBoxMaterial, MainBoxMaterial, MainBoxMaterial, MainBoxMaterial, 4,hh, 90-alpha, hh, dx, dx, 15, dx, B-dx, 15, A-dx, B-dx, 15, A-dx, dx, 15
dx2 = dx + hh * SIN(alpha) LIN_ A-dx2, dx2, hh, A-dx2, B-dx2, hh DEL 1 ENDIF
IF objType = 2 THEN ! Water Flow Indicator ROTy 90 CIRCLE ConWidth_1/2 DEL 1
MATERIAL MainBoxMaterial
ROTz 90 ROTx 90 ADDz -0.4*A
hy1 = 0.20*ConWidth_1 hy2 = 0.60*ConWidth_1 hy22= 0.52*ConWidth_1 hy3 = 0.80*ConWidth_1 hx = SQR((ConWidth_1/2)^2-hy1^2)
PRISM_ 11, 0.8*A, -B/2+hy1, hy1, 15, -B/2, hy2, 15, -ConWidth_1/2, hy2, 15, -ConWidth_1/3, hy3, 15, ConWidth_1/3, hy3, 15, ConWidth_1/2, hy2, 15, B/2, hy2, 15, B/2-hy1, hy1, 15, hx, hy1, 79, 0,0,979, -hx, hy1, 3015 DEL 3
RR = 0.08*ConWidth_1 ROTx 180 REVOLVE 2,180,1+2+16+32, 0,0.55*ConWidth_1+RR, 901, RR,360,4001 DEL 1 ADDy 0.55*ConWidth_1+RR CYLIND hy1, RR DEL 1 ADDy -0.55*ConWidth_1-RR CYLIND hy1, RR DEL 1
RESOL 6 ADDz hy3 CYLIND 0.1*ZZYZX,0.25*A ADDz 0.1*ZZYZX ROTx 90 ROTy 90 ADDz -A/2 PRISM 4,A, -meterW/2, 0, -meterW/2, 0.9*ZZYZX-hy3, meterW/2, 0.9*ZZYZX-hy3, meterW/2, 0 DEL 5 ENDIF
IF objType = 3 THEN ! Water Motor Alarm tck = 0.1*A
ADDz ZZYZX-B/2 ROTy 90 ADDz -A/2 CYLIND tck, B/2 DEL 2
ROTy 90 ADDz -A/2+tck ROTz 90 HOTSPOT 0,B/2,0, unID: unID=unID+1 PRISM_ 4,0.9*A, -0.47*B, -ZZYZX+B/2, 15, -0.47*B, 0, 79, 0.47*B, 0, 1079, 0.47*B, -ZZYZX+B/2, 15 DEL 3 ENDIF ENDIF
DEL TOP RESOL res
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, cShow3D = 1, gs_ConMat = MainBoxMaterial, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show_3D = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConPosZ_1=ConPosZ_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = 1 END
Symbol.Script_2D:
! Fire Detect and Alarm Equipment DrawingNum = 1
! --- OTHER VIEWS --- !
ROT2 (SYMB_MIRRORED - NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED)) * (DrawingNum > 1) * SYMB_ROTANGLE
IF DrawingNum = 2 THEN PROJECT2 -3, 90, 2 ! Bottom IF DrawingNum = 3 THEN PROJECT2 4, 270, 2 ! Front IF DrawingNum = 4 THEN PROJECT2 4, 90, 2 ! Back IF DrawingNum = 5 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * SYMB_MIRRORED, 2 ! Right IF DrawingNum = 6 THEN PROJECT2 4, 180 * NOT(SYMB_MIRRORED), 2 ! Left
unID = 1
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
IF objType = 1 OR objType = 3 THEN ! Alarm Pressure Switch and Water Motor Alarm ConEdit_1 = 0 ENDIF
IF objType = 2 THEN ! Water Flow Indicato ConEdit_1 = 1 ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, MEP_NumConnectionData = gs_Connections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, DrawingNum = DrawingNum, MEP_InsShow = 0, MEP_cline_show = 0, gs_cont_pen = gs_cont_pen, gs_fill_type=gs_fill_type, gs_fill_pen=gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen=gs_back_pen, ConPosX_1=ConPosX_1, ConPosY_1=ConPosY_1, ConLength_1=ConLength_1, ConEdit_1 = ConEdit_1 DEL 1
PEN gs_cont_pen SET FILL gs_fill_type
DrawingNum = 1 IF DrawingNum = 1 AND GLOB_CONTEXT <> 22 THEN ! Top
! --- FIRE DETECTION AND ALARM EQUIPMENT --- !
HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 IF objType = 1 THEN ! Alarm Pressure Switch ADD2 -A/2, -A/2
HOTSPOT2 A, 0, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0,0, unID: unID=unID+1
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, 0,0, 1, 0, B, 1, A, B, 1, A, 0, 1
POLY2 4, 5, dx, dx, dx, B-dx, A-dx, B-dx, A-dx, dx
POLY2 4, 5, dx2, dx2, dx2, B-dx2, A-dx2, B-dx2, A-dx2, dx2
LINE2 dx,dx, dx2,dx2 LINE2 A-dx,dx, A-dx2,dx2 LINE2 dx,B-dx, dx2,B-dx2 LINE2 A-dx,B-dx, A-dx2,B-dx2 DEL 1 ENDIF
IF objType = 2 THEN ! Water Flow Indicator HOTSPOT2 -0.4*A, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0.4*A, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -0.4*A, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0.4*A, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1
POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A/2, -meterW/2, 1, -A/2, meterW/2, 1, A/2, meterW/2, 1, A/2, -meterW/2, 1 POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -0.4*A, -B/2, 1, -0.4*A, -meterW/2, 1, 0.4*A, -meterW/2, 1, 0.4*A, -B/2, 1 POLY2_B 4, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -0.4*A, B/2, 1, -0.4*A, meterW/2, 1, 0.4*A, meterW/2, 1, 0.4*A, B/2, 1 ENDIF
IF objType = 3 THEN ! Water Motor Alarm tck = 0.1*A HOTSPOT2 -A/2, B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -A/2, -B/2, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, 0.47*B, unID: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 A/2, -0.47*B, unID: unID=unID+1
POLY2_B 8, 1+2+4+64, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -A/2, B/2, 1, -A/2+tck, B/2, 0, -A/2+tck, 0.47*B, 1, A/2, 0.47*B, 1, A/2, -0.47*B, 1, -A/2+tck, -0.47*B, 0, -A/2+tck, -B/2, 1, -A/2, -B/2, 1 LINE2 -A/2+tck, B/2, -A/2+tck, -B/2 ENDIF ENDIF DEL TOP
END
Symbol.Script_1D:
! Fire Detect and Alarm Equipment
EPS = 0.0001
DIM type_dim[3] type_dim[1]=`Сигнальный Мембранный Переключатель` type_dim[2]=`Индикатор Потока Воды` type_dim[3]=`Сигнализация водяного мотора`
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "objTypeStr" THEN IF objTypeStr = type_dim[1] THEN objType = 1 IF objTypeStr = type_dim[2] THEN objType = 2 IF objTypeStr = type_dim[3] THEN objType = 3 PARAMETERS objType = objType ENDIF
IF objTypeStr <> type_dim[objType] THEN objTypeStr = type_dim[objType] PARAMETERS objTypeStr = objTypeStr ENDIF
! --- HARDCODED AND DERIVED VARIABLES --- !
neckH = 0.25*ZZYZX bottomThk = 0.10*ZZYZX alpha = 5 dx = 0.05*A dx2 = dx+(ZZYZX-neckH-bottomThk)*SIN(alpha)
meterW = B/3 ! Water Flow Indicator width
z = 0
PARAMETERS ac_toplevel = z PARAMETERS ac_bottomlevel = z

Symbol.Script_VL:
! Fire Detect and Alarm Equipment
call "FM_types_MEP" parameters DIM shape_typ_to_validation[3] shape_typ_to_validation[1] = 0 ! Rectangle shape_typ_to_validation[2] = 1 ! Circle shape_typ_to_validation[3] = 0 ! Oval
IF GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" OR gs_detlevel_3D_m = -1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 ! Detailed IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 IF gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` THEN gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m ELSE IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Откл.` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Простой` IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN gs_detlevel_3D = `Детальный` PARAMETERS gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D ENDIF
VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D" `Детальный`,`Простой`,`Откл.` VALUES "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 2, 1, 0
! --- OBJECT SPECIFIC PARAMETERS --- !
VALUES "objType" 1, 2, 3 VALUES "objTypeStr" type_dim
! --- CONNECTIONS --- !
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN IF objType = 1 THEN ! Alarm Pressure Switch hh = ZZYZX - neckH - bottomThk dy = hh * TAN(alpha)
IF A < 2*ConWidth_1 THEN A = 2*ConWidth_1 VALUES "A" RANGE [2*ConWidth_1,] IF B < ConWidth_1+A/2 THEN B = ConWidth_1+A/2 VALUES "B" RANGE [ConWidth_1+A/2,] IF ZZYZX < 0.01 THEN ZZYZX = 0.01 VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [0.01,]
VALUES "A" RANGE [2*ConWidth_1,] VALUES "B" RANGE [ConWidth_1+A/2,] VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [0.01,] ENDIF
IF objType = 2 THEN ! Water Flow Indicator minW = ConWidth_1 IF A<minW THEN A=minW PARAMETERS A=minW ENDIF VALUES "A" RANGE [minW,] IF B < 2*ConWidth_1 THEN B = 2*ConWidth_1 VALUES "B" RANGE [2*ConWidth_1,] IF ZZYZX < 2*ConWidth_1 THEN ZZYZX = 2*ConWidth_1 VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [2*ConWidth_1,]
VALUES "A" RANGE [ConWidth_1,] VALUES "B" RANGE [2*ConWidth_1,] VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [2*ConWidth_1,]
R = ZZYZX/10 ENDIF
IF objType = 3 THEN ! Water Motor Alarm IF A < 1.5*ConWidth_1 THEN A = 1.5*ConWidth_1 VALUES "A" RANGE [1.5*ConWidth_1,] IF B < (ConWidth_1/2)/(2*0.47) THEN B = (ConWidth_1/2)/(2*0.47) VALUES "B" RANGE [(ConWidth_1/2)/(2*0.47),] IF ZZYZX < B THEN ZZYZX = B VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [B,]
VALUES "A" RANGE [ConWidth_1,] VALUES "B" RANGE [(ConWidth_1/2)/(2*0.47),] VALUES "ZZYZX" RANGE [B,] ENDIF ENDIF
PARAMETERS MEP_NumberConnections = 1
! --- CONNECTION --- !
ConID = 1 ConName = `Соединение Трубы`
IF objType = 1 OR objType = 3 THEN ConDVecX = 0 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = -1
ConWVecX = 1 ConWVecY = 0 ConWVecZ = 0 ENDIF
IF objType = 2 THEN ConDVecX = -1 ConDVecY = 0 ConDVecZ = 0
ConWVecX = 0 ConWVecY = 1 ConWVecZ = 0 ENDIF
IF NOT(SetProgram) THEN VALUES "ConLength_1" RANGE [0,] VALUES "ConWidth_1" RANGE (0, ) VALUES "ConDepth_1" RANGE (0, )
IF ConWidth_1<EPS THEN ConWidth_1=EPS PARAMETERS ConWidth_1=EPS ENDIF
ConPosX_1 = 0 PARAMETERS ConPosX_1 = ConPosX_1 ConPosY_1 = 0 PARAMETERS ConPosY_1 = ConPosY_1 ConPosZ_1 = 0 PARAMETERS ConPosZ_1 = ConPosZ_1
VALUES "ConWallThickness_1" RANGE [0, ConWidth_1/2] ENDIF
CALL "MEP_m_ConnectionsMEP_4" PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram, gs_Connections = gs_Connections, MEP_NumConnectionData = MEP_NumConnectionData, MEP_StrConnectionData = MEP_StrConnectionData, MEP_NumberConnections = MEP_NumberConnections, gs_AddConnections = gs_AddConnections, ConName = ConName, ConID = ConID, ConPosX = ConPosX_1, ConPosY = ConPosY_1, ConPosZ = ConPosZ_1, ConDVecX = ConDVecX, ConDVecY = ConDVecY, ConDVecZ = ConDVecZ, ConWVecX = ConWVecX, ConWVecY = ConWVecY, ConWVecZ = ConWVecZ,
ConNominalWidth = ConNominalWidth_1, ConNominalDepth = ConNominalDepth_1, ConWidth = ConWidth_1, ConDepth = ConDepth_1, ConLength = ConLength_1, ConWallThickness = ConWallThickness_1, ConConnectorWidth = ConConnectorWidth_1, ConConnectorDepth = ConConnectorDepth_1, ConConnectorWidth2 = ConConnectorWidth2_1, ConToolType = ConToolType_1, ConStatus = ConStatus_1, ConType_1 = ConType_1, ConConnectorType_1 = ConConnectorType_1, ConSystem_1 = ConSystem_1, ui_page_idx = ui_page_idx, ui_current_con = ui_current_con, shape_typ_to_validation = shape_typ_to_validation, MEP_enabled_geometry_mod = 1, bUIConnectionStatusCheckbox = 1
PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][1] = STR(ConToolType_1, 1, 0) PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][2] = ConName PARAMETERS MEP_ConInfo[ConID][3] = "0"
IF setProgram THEN SetProgram = 0 PARAMETERS SetProgram = SetProgram ENDIF
